  "description": "A unique refrigerator of its kind, which, in addition to advanced equipment and thoughtful ergonomics, also boasts the possibility of styling with special decorative panels, which allows you to “modify” the appearance of the device in such a way as to best match the interior of the kitchen. SpaceMax technology provides better thermal insulation of the walls, thanks to which the model boasts an increased chamber capacity while maintaining the typical dimensions of the case. Among other things, the Samsung BeSpoke RB34A6B4FAP refrigerator boasts a reliable inverter compressor, separate cooling circuits for each of the chambers, as well as full support for Full No Frost technology, which prevents the formation of ice and frost inside. The total useful volume of the model is 340 liters. The refrigerator compartment boasts a special adjustable humidity zone (Humidity Fresh +), a bottle shelf, as well as an advanced All-Around Cooling dynamic cooling system. The 112 l freezer is located below and features support for the Power Freeze function. The back panel of the refrigerator is a completely flat protective cover that looks as neat as possible, is easy to clean and provides additional durability to the device.",
